<!--
    employee.xml

    This file plays the role of the "spring xml configuration" referred
    to in the exercise. It contains:
      - Two departments (IT, HR) - "Create one or two more departments"
      - Four employee instances  - "Create four more instances of Employee"
    Each employee reuses one of the two departments and has a list of
    skills, exactly as required by the exercise.
-->
